    "en": {
      "title": "\"Araliyagaha Mandir is not in a condition to go\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The new Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena said that the Araliyagaha Mandir is still not ready to go.",
        "He said that it is not possible to create a clear picture of a country from one or two incidents and stated that the government is working in accordance with the constitution.",
        "The Prime Minister said that before talking about the international, we should know about the interior of the country and the government is working to get the support of foreign countries.",
        "He also stated that a country cannot move without a stable government."
      ],
